{"title":"两弦的马头琴","authors":["李建华"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":11,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"两弦的马头琴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李建华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何必要那么多根弦呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杂乱的，永远不会是美好的乐章！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，你只需要两根弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条，是激情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远弹奏出一个古老民族的豪放；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条，是深沉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹奏的是永无止境的向往！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你狂奔的马蹄声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你深情的浅吟低唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在这两根弦上欢快地蹦呢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别小看这两根弦的威力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不信，你轻轻地弹一声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便能呼唤所有的草原小草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——齐唱！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}